      "span_text": "The birth weight charts for US babies with Down syndrome derived by [CITATION_1] gave similar results to ours (e.g., at 38 weeks gestation median birth weight for boys was 3,048 g vs. 2,947 g in this study and for girls 3,092 g vs. 3,019 g)."
